{"tid":1408602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工同塞地鐵好似有矛盾。","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:15:33.000Z","uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45b87b0a29a531393502c0a9b2b0870b0293238d","tid":1408602,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"聽朝全港罷工， 地鐵內可能唔夠人坐， 車箱內會好空洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班波板糖 ，咁多空位會推你入去。<br />\n<br />\n另外各位留意返， 有啲好想返工嘅人會屌鬼，<br />\n可能到時難以再有一班人講支持。 因為本身支持後生仔嗰班全部喺屋企罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以聽朝你哋未必塞得到條鐵路。<br />\n就算係塞到，所受嘅群眾壓力都會比對上兩次大得多。<br />\n<br />\n而且依家每一區都有人行緊街， 聽朝一早塞開既，好有可能未訓醒，唔夠人。<br />\n<br />\n所以聽朝自己執生， 我就準備瞓覺啦，早點起身陪大家一齊坐地鐵返工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb412c843e1387297dda81f8074603ac8a28e40a","tid":1408602,"uid":51848,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xOpkB4N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxOpkB4N.png&h=e9d2533f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea1f6375f2362b043ff23083321c416b37971ef8","tid":1408602,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"鳩sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果晚你屌果個女警有冇後續呀<br />\n想睇甜故"},{"pid":"5d0fa453f72f4c68e65260aa7ff6d8aa7ed373e7","tid":1408602,"uid":254022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收皮啦，諗定聽日點安排人手啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"1531a290690e04c5791407d68d774a77b2d45421","tid":1408602,"uid":234789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:47:21.000Z","msg":"8月5 塞東鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/M2KLPxP4sqS1kWB_cN7KTw\" d